  "detailed_description": "Psycho Squirrels is a 2D platforming, puzzle game where players must navigate squirrels through a variety of stages to collect acorns before winter arrives.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThese city squirrels have been slacking off and aren't prepared for winter. They need your help as they head out into the world in search of delicious acorns.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Help the squirrels collect enough acorns before winter arrives.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Use the local flora and fauna to guide your squirrels to their goals.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Navigate through over 50 puzzling stages plus bonus stages.",
